Project: COAB Platform (Chile)

- All UI, messages, DB schema in Spanish (es-CL).
- Enforce Chilean RUT validation (XX.XXX.XXX-X, mod 11).
- Currency: CLP with dot thousands, e.g. $1.234.567.
- Dates: dd/MM/yyyy or "d de MMMM a las HH:mm" (date-fns es locale).
- Database uses Spanish table/column names.
- Backend: Node 22, Express/Fastify, TypeScript, Prisma, PostgreSQL (Supabase).
- Frontend: Next.js/Vite, TypeScript, shadcn/ui, Tailwind, mobile-first.
- Security: JWT (access/refresh) with rotation, rate limits, helmet, HTTPS.
- Never commit .env or secrets; keep environment per service.
- Source of truth: IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md; see CURSOR.md for details.

When generating code:
- Respect Spanish naming and Chilean formats (RUT, CLP, dates).
